# I have successfully moved to the nearest iron ore patch.
# 
# Now, I will harvest iron ore to ensure I have enough for smelting into iron plates.

harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.IronOre), quantity=10)  # Harvesting 10 iron ore from the iron ore patch.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Checking the updated inventory after harvesting.
